metadata.name: Graffe #1
metadata.description:
✨ Powered by NFT-Inator. Crеate уour own no-code collection for free at nft-inator.com!

2999 Graffes survived the Web3 planetary crisis that occurred in 2999, eating from the few remaining trees in the Ethereum Blockchain, increasingly tall and with few leaves. They are among us to warn us to respect the Web3 Planet, reminding us how the real and the imaginary world follow the same course. It's a roadmap in reverse. The only utility is respect for the planet, with Graffes as a symbol
